snippet.title: Johnny Depp Has Multiple Witnesses Who Testified They Saw Amber with No Visible Injuries
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and his legal team have interviewed multiple people, under oath, that testified to details surrounding Amber Heard‘s domestic accusations that he believes it proves the alleged acts and injuries were a hoax.

In transcripts obtained by The Blast, four employees and one neighbor from the ex-couple’s residential building were deposed regarding any signs they may have seen between the stars, including the interactions with Heard where all five claims she had no visible injuries.
